#1F2937; font-size: 14px;\">Enable two-factor authentication</span></div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: #10B981; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 12px;\">âœ“</span><span style=\"color: #1F2937; font-size: 14px;\">Never share your admin credentials</span></div><div><span style=\"color: #10B981; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 12px;\">âœ“</span><span style=\"color: #1F2937; font-size: 14px;\">Review account activity regularly</span></div></div><div style=\"background: #F3F4F6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0;\"><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: #1F2937; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;\">âš ï¸ Important</p><p style=\"margin: 0; color: #6B7280; font-size: 14px;\">If you did not request this password reset, please contact the security team immediately at <a href=\"mailto:{{supportEmail}}\" style=\"color: {{primaryColor}}; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;\">{{supportEmail}}</a></p></div>"
  },
  {
