    "bodyContent": "<h1 style=\"font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; margin: 0 0 16px 0; color: #1F2937;\">ğŸ”„ Role Update</h1><p style=\"color: #6B7280; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 32px 0;\">Hi {{adminName}}, your admin role has been updated.</p><div style=\"background: #EFF6FF; border-left: 4px solid #3B82F6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #1E40AF; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;\">ğŸ“‹ Role Change Details</h3><table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\"><tr><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; color: #1E40AF; font-size: 14px;\">Previous Role</td><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: 600; color: #1E40AF;\">{{oldRole}}</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; color: #1E40AF; font-size: 14px;\">New Role</td><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: 700; color: #10B981; font-size: 16px;\">{{newRole}}</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; color: #1E40AF; font-size: 14px;\">Changed By</td><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: 600; color: #1E40AF;\">{{changedBy}}</td></tr></table></div><div style=\"background: #F9FAFB; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin: 24px 0;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #1F2937; font-weight: 600;\">ğŸ“ Reason for Change</h3><p style=\"margin: 0; color: #6B7280; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">{{reason}}</p></div><div style=\"background: #ECFDF5; border-left: 4px solid #10B981; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #065F46; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;\">âœ… What This Means</h3><p style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #065F46; font-size: 14px;\">Your access permissions and capabilities within the admin panel have been updated according to your new role.</p><p style=\"margin: 0; color: #065F46; font-size: 14px;\">Please review your new permissions and contact support if you have any questions.</p></div><div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;\"><a href=\"{{adminDashboard}}\" style=\"display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #06B6D4 0%, #0891B2 100%); color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;\">Go to Admin Panel</a></div><div style=\"background: #F3F4F6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0; text-align: center;\"><p style=\"margin: 0; color: #6B7280; font-size: 14px;\">Questions? Contact us at <a href=\"mailto:{{supportEmail}}\" style=\"color: {{primaryColor}}; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;\">{{supportEmail}}</a></p></div>"
  },
  {
    "key": "ADMIN_ACCOUNT_SUSPENDED",
    "name": "Admin Account Suspended",
    "description": "Notification when admin account is suspended",
    "category": "SYSTEM",
    "subject": "âš ï¸ Your Admin Account Has Been Suspended - {{brandName}}",
    "preheader": "Your administrative access has been temporarily suspended",
    "layout": "default",
    "variables": ["adminName", "reason", "suspendedBy", "suspendedAt", "contactEmail", "brandName", "brandLogo", "primaryColor", "supportEmail", "supportPhone"],
    "bodyContent": "<h1 style=\"font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; margin: 0 0 16px 0; color: #1F2937;\">âš ï¸ Account Suspended</h1><p style=\"color: #6B7280; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 32px 0;\">Hi {{adminName}}, your admin account has been suspended.</p><div style=\"background: #FEF2F2; border-left: 4px solid #EF4444; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #991B1B; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;\">ğŸš« Suspension Notice</h3><p style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #991B1B; font-size: 14px;\">Your administrative access to {{brandName}} has been temporarily suspended.</p><table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 16px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; color: #991B1B; font-size: 14px;\">Suspended By</td><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: 600; color: #991B1B;\">{{suspendedBy}}</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; color: #991B1B; font-size: 14px;\">Date & Time</td><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: 600; color: #991B1B;\">{{suspendedAt}}</td></tr></table></div><div style=\"background: #F9FAFB; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin: 24px 0;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #1F2937; font-weight: 600;\">ğŸ“ Reason for Suspension</h3><p style=\"margin: 0; color: #6B7280; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">{{reason}}</p></div><div style=\"background: #FEF3C7; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #92400E; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;\">âš ï¸ What This Means</h3><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: #92400E; font-size: 14px;\">â€¢ You cannot access the admin panel</p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: #92400E; font-size: 14px;\">â€¢ All administrative privileges are temporarily revoked</p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: #92400E; font-size: 14px;\">â€¢ Your account data remains secure</p><p style=\"margin: 0; color: #92400E; font-size: 14px;\">â€¢ You will be notified when your account is reactivated</p></div><div style=\"background: #EFF6FF; border-left: 4px solid #3B82F6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #1E40AF; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;\">ğŸ“ Need to Appeal?</h3><p style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #1E40AF; font-size: 14px;\">If you believe this suspension was made in error or would like to discuss this matter, please contact:</p><p style=\"margin: 0; color: #1E40AF; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;\"><a href=\"mailto:{{contactEmail}}\" style=\"color: #1E40AF; text-decoration: none;\">{{contactEmail}}</a></p></div><div style=\"background: #F3F4F6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0; text-align: center;\"><p style=\"margin: 0; color: #6B7280; font-size: 14px;\">For urgent matters, contact: <a href=\"mailto:{{supportEmail}}\" style=\"color: {{primaryColor}}; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;\">{{supportEmail}}</a></p></div>"
  },
  {
    "key": "ADMIN_ACCOUNT_REACTIVATED",
    "name": "Admin Account Reactivated",
    "description": "Notification when suspended admin account is reactivated",
    "category": "SYSTEM",
    "subject": "âœ… Your Admin Account Has Been Reactivated - {{brandName}}",
    "preheader": "Your administrative access has been restored",
    "layout": "default",
    "variables": ["adminName", "reactivatedBy", "reactivatedAt", "adminDashboard", "brandName", "brandLogo", "primaryColor", "supportEmail", "supportPhone"],
    "bodyContent": "<h1 style=\"font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; margin: 0 0 16px 0; color: #1F2937;\">âœ… Account Reactivated</h1><p style=\"color: #6B7280; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 32px 0;\">Hi {{adminName}}, your admin account has been reactivated!</p><div style=\"background: #ECFDF5; border-left: 4px solid #10B981; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #065F46; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;\">ğŸ‰ Welcome Back!</h3><p style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #065F46; font-size: 14px;\">Your administrative access to {{brandName}} has been fully restored.</p><table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 16px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; color: #065F46; font-size: 14px;\">Reactivated By</td><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: 600; color: #065F46;\">{{reactivatedBy}}</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; color: #065F46; font-size: 14px;\">Date & Time</td><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: 600; color: #065F46;\">{{reactivatedAt}}</td></tr></table></div><div style=\"background: #F9FAFB; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin: 24px 0;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 18px; color: #1F2937; font-weight: 600;\">âœ“ Your Access Has Been Restored</h3><div style=\"margin-bottom: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: #10B981; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 12px;\">âœ“</span><span style=\"color: #1F2937; font-size: 14px;\">Full admin panel access</span></div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: #10B981; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 12px;\">âœ“</span><span style=\"color: #1F2937; font-size: 14px;\">All administrative privileges</span></div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: #10B981; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 12px;\">âœ“</span><span style=\"color: #1F2937; font-size: 14px;\">System management capabilities</span></div><div><span style=\"color: #10B981; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 12px;\">âœ“</span><span style=\"color: #1F2937; font-size: 14px;\">User and order management</span></div></div><div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;\"><a href=\"{{adminDashboard}}\" style=\"display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10B981 0%, #059669 100%); color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;\">Access Admin Panel</a></div><div style=\"background: #EFF6FF; border-left: 4px solid #3B82F6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #1E40AF; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;\">ğŸ” Security Reminder</h3><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: #1E40AF; font-size: 14px;\">Please ensure you:</p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 4px 0; color: #1E40AF; font-size: 14px;\">â€¢ Review and follow all security policies</p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 4px 0; color: #1E40AF; font-size: 14px;\">â€¢ Use strong authentication methods</p><p style=\"margin: 0; color: #1E40AF; font-size: 14px;\">â€¢ Report any suspicious activity immediately</p></div><div style=\"background: #F3F4F6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0; text-align: center;\"><p style=\"margin: 0; color: #6B7280; font-size: 14px;\">Questions? Contact us at <a href=\"mailto:{{supportEmail}}\" style=\"color: {{primaryColor}}; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;\">{{supportEmail}}</a></p></div>"
  },
  {
    "key": "ADMIN_2FA_ENABLED",
    "name": "Admin 2FA Enabled",
    "description": "Confirmation when admin enables two-factor authentication",
    "category": "SYSTEM",
    "subject": "ğŸ” Two-Factor Authentication Enabled - {{brandName}}",
    "preheader": "Your admin account security has been enhanced",
    "layout": "default",
    "variables": ["adminName", "enabledAt", "method", "backupCodes", "adminDashboard", "brandName", "brandLogo", "primaryColor", "supportEmail", "supportPhone"],
    "bodyContent": "<h1 style=\"font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; margin: 0 0 16px 0; color: #1F2937;\">ğŸ” 2FA Enabled</h1><p style=\"color: #6B7280; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 32px 0;\">Hi {{adminName}}, two-factor authentication is now active on your admin account.</p><div style=\"background: #ECFDF5; border-left: 4px solid #10B981; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #065F46; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;\">âœ… Security Enhanced</h3><p style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #065F46; font-size: 14px;\">Your admin account is now protected with two-factor authentication.</p><table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 16px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; color: #065F46; font-size: 14px;\">Method</td><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: 600; color: #065F46;\">{{method}}</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; color: #065F46; font-size: 14px;\">Enabled At</td><td style=\"padding: 8px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: 600; color: #065F46;\">{{enabledAt}}</td></tr></table></div><div style=\"background: #F9FAFB; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin: 24px 0;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 18px; color: #1F2937; font-weight: 600;\">ğŸ”‘ Backup Codes</h3><p style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #6B7280; font-size: 14px;\">Save these backup codes in a secure location. You can use them to access your account if you lose your authentication device.</p><div style=\"background: white; border: 2px dashed #E5E7EB; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0;\"><code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; color: #1F2937; line-height: 2;\">{{backupCodes}}</code></div><p style=\"margin: 0; color: #EF4444; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;\">âš ï¸ Each code can only be used once. Store them securely!</p></div><div style=\"background: #EFF6FF; border-left: 4px solid #3B82F6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #1E40AF; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;\">ğŸ“± What Happens Next?</h3><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: #1E40AF; font-size: 14px;\">From now on, when you log in to your admin account, you will need to:</p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 4px 0; color: #1E40AF; font-size: 14px;\">1. Enter your password</p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 4px 0; color: #1E40AF; font-size: 14px;\">2. Provide your 2FA code from your authenticator app</p><p style=\"margin: 0; color: #1E40AF; font-size: 14px;\">3. Access the admin panel securely</p></div><div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;\"><a href=\"{{adminDashboard}}\" style=\"display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #06B6D4 0%, #0891B2 100%); color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;\">Go to Admin Panel</a></div><div style=\"background: #FEF2F2; border-left: 4px solid #EF4444; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0;\"><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-weight: 600; color: #991B1B; font-size: 14px;\">âš ï¸ Security Notice</p><p style=\"margin: 0; color: #991B1B; font-size: 14px;\">If you did not enable 2FA, please contact security immediately at <a href=\"mailto:{{supportEmail}}\" style=\"color: #991B1B; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;\">{{supportEmail}}</a></p></div>"
  },
  {
